data.message:
My Rap Verse inspired by #Eminem 

This ain’t a rap battle
Or will you leave my cage rattle 
The only way you’re going to beat me
Is if my name is Hillary 
So you better bring all of your artillery
Plus get the help of the Russians
Because that’s the only way 
You’re going to “Trump” me
And stump me with your corruption
Or get the jump on me 
Because ever since I blew up onto this scene 
I’ve been a volcano eruption
Burning through my competition
Like human combustion
So fuck clutching your chest 
Because this is more than a heart attack
Or a concussion if I must confess 
If anything I’m an aneurysm 
Just waiting to attack 
And you’re full of shit
That I must be flushing
